g.text: and Unassociated Causes/Risks of Deaths in India
* Source: Global Burden of Disease (https://vizhub.healthdata.org/gbd-results/) causes and risks data and WHO Life Tables
(https://apps.who.int/gho/data/node.main.LIFECOUNTRY?lang=en) were used combined with the Life table method to arrive at these
results. 'PM2.5 relative to WHO Guideline' bar displays life years lost relative to the WHO guideline as calculated by latest AQLI
(2021) data, which will be published in September 2023.
